支槍佢地好大鑊</blockquote><br />\n咁最後咪保得住人地保唔住自己囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4b48e69845fc43c72823042221fca32e572d3b","tid":208433,"uid":86578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T15:21:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今次走得甩 都唔會次次咁好彩啦<br />\n佢而家話哂都保住個名無殺死過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁做得呢啲嘢唔係諗住仲可以全身而去呀嘛"},{"pid":"b47e05361736d8baebb820082c4c3e1eb9fc8252","tid":208433,"uid":1408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T15:38:19.000Z","msg":"遲早落網啦<br />\n睇幾時嘅姐"},{"pid":"e8645aafa2a9ff0f2bd7fe372ebac6ccc9af141a","tid":208433,"uid":57331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T15:42:32.000Z","msg":"又開始吹奏"},{"pid":"fb66a44ac1213dea915dfceb41ef224e4c77fee1","tid":208433,"uid":43993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T15:49:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>翁續指，當日隨後一部小巴駛至，葉的2名同黨率先上車，殿後的葉轉身上車時，就遭其中一名警員開槍擊中背部，最終被捕，「佢個人相當重承諾，一直諗係咪佢一念之間，太過『仁慈』最終付出後果」。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同黑警講仁慈？<br />\n<br />\n沒有一個黑警係無辜的<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同賊講仁慈咪一撚樣on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef19b0e61765e6d11e5ac186d0b50542294db6ca","tid":208433,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T15:51:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遲早落網啦<br />\n睇幾時嘅姐</blockquote><br />\n於B, 成日見到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d02f7e3709b59f9a5b5db6d15519da23c33f58","tid":208433,"uid":1408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T15:55